videos.description: UConn's Gabby Williams knifes inside the lane and scores between a couple South Carolina defenders.
videos.headline: Williams finishes tough lay-in between a couple defenders

videos.description: South Carolina's A'ja Wilson catches a pass up court, lays it in and draws the foul.
videos.headline: Wilson races up court to score and-1

videos.description: Off of a miss, Crystal Dangerfield heads up court then dishes to Napheesa Collier who lays it in.
videos.headline: Nice pass from Dangerfield sets up a UConn score

videos.description: UConn's Napheesa Collier steals a pass then lays it in as the Huskies head to the locker room on a 7-0 run.
videos.headline: Collier gets steal and lay-in for UConn

videos.description: UConn head coach Geno Auriemma on what his team needs to do to hold on and win in the second half.
videos.headline: UConn head coach Geno Auriemma on what his team needs to do to hold on and win in the second half.

videos.description: South Carolina head coach Dawn Staley on what her team is doing well and what they need to improve on in the second half
videos.headline: South Carolina head coach Dawn Staley on what her team is doing well and what they need to improve on in the second half

videos.description: In transition, Katie Lou Samuelson bounces to Saniya Chong who scores plus the foul.
videos.headline: Samuelson assist sets up Chong three-point play

videos.description: In transition, the Huskies share the ball, eventually getting it to Napheesa Collier who scores and draws the foul.
videos.headline: Great ball movement leads to a UConn bucket and-1

videos.description: As the shot clock winds down, Crystal Dangerfield dishes to Natalie Butler who lays it in.
videos.headline: Dangerfield gives to Butler who scores and beats the shot clock

videos.description: The clock winds down sealing UConn's 100th consecutive win with a victory over South Carolina.
videos.headline: UConn makes it 100 straight wins

videos.description: UConn's Gabby Williams talks about her performance and her emotions after the Huskies' 100th straight win.
videos.headline: Williams: 'This program is something special'

videos.description: Reaction to UConn's 100th straight win and the legacy Geno Auriemma and the Huskies' program has left
videos.headline: Reaction to UConn's 100th straight win and the legacy Geno Auriemma and the Huskies' program has left

videos.description: UConn women's basketball extends their record win streak to 100 games with another big win on Monday.
videos.headline: UConn's road to 100 in a row

videos.description: Gabby Williams' big game of 26 points and 14 rebounds propels No. 1 UConn to  66-55 victory against No. 6 South Carolina, the Huskies' 100th consecutive victory.
videos.headline: UConn tops South Carolina for 100th straight win

videos.description: Connecticut coach Geno Auriemma is proud of his team for reaching 100 straight wins but knows there isn't a medal at the end of 100, that medal comes in March.
